Name: Average time from 'Accepted + In Progress' to 'Completed + Cancelled'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Completed + Cancelled'

Name: Average time from 'Completed + Cancelled' to 'Completed + Resolved'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Completed + Cancelled' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Total time for 'Completed + Cancelled' cases
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Completed + Cancelled and the end of the case

Name: Average resolution time of 'Completed + Cancelled' before reaching 'Completed + Closed'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Completed + Cancelled' and activity 'Completed + Closed'

Name: Total time from 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' to 'Completed + Cancelled'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Completed + Cancelled'

Name: Average waiting time to 'Completed + Cancelled' after 'Accepted + Wait - User'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - User' and activity 'Completed + Cancelled'

Name: Total resolution time of 'Completed + Cancelled' after 'Accepted + Assigned'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and activity 'Completed + Cancelled'

Name: Minimum time from 'Accepted + In Progress' to 'Completed + Cancelled'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Completed + Cancelled'

Name: Average time it takes 'Completed + Cancelled' to be done after 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' and activity 'Completed + Cancelled'

Name: Minimum resolution time of 'Completed + Cancelled' before 'Completed + In Call'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Completed + Cancelled' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Average time from 'Completed + Cancelled' to the next activity
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Completed + Cancelled and the end of the case

Name: Average time for 'Completed + Cancelled' to occur after any 'Accepted + Wait' status
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Completed + Cancelled'

Name: Minimum time it takes 'Completed + Cancelled' after 'Completed + In Call'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Completed + In Call' and activity 'Completed + Cancelled'

Name: Average time to 'Completed + Cancelled' from the start of the case
Metric: The average of the duration between the start of the case and activity 'Completed + Cancelled'

Name: Total time since 'Completed + Cancelled' and 'Completed + Resolved' are performed
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Completed + Cancelled' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Minimum time for 'Completed + Cancelled' to occur after 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Completed + Cancelled'

Name: 'Completed + Cancelled' Cycle Time
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Completed + Cancelled and the end of the case
